You need python3 and pip3 for this

To install run:
python3 setup.py install

With optional flags:
--prefix DIRECTORY      :  Local install in DIRECTORY
--coptionsi "OPTIONS"   :  Options for ./configure e.g. CC=clang (only if gsl is to be installed)
--install_reqs          :  Installing requirements
--tests                 :  Installing testsuite with pip3
--pipoptions  "OPTIONS" :  Extra options for pip3
--verbose               :  Verbose installation
